	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=2900&amp;mid=106020183659838">Confirmation of heart</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=2900&amp;mid=106020183659838#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Wed, Aug 6th 4:39 PM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=94482"><span id=" ">Artane</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">12 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Just confirming this heart does drop in the room to the right of &quot;The Bar.&quot;<br/><br/>Level 40 wizard here.. ran in self buffed with tboots on.&nbsp;&nbsp;Found the inferno goblin wizard standing there in the room to the right as everyone has said.  Rooted and nuked him down where he stood.  Looted and ran to zone.  No heart this time.  Medded back up and did it again.  Respawn of another inferno goblin wizard was there, rooted, nuked down, looted the heart and ran to zone.  Zoned that time with 13 percent health because another goblin snuck up on me when I wasn't watching.  All in all, it took no time to get the heart.  Thanks for the helpful posts everyone. :)<br/><br/>Aabren</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
